Preheat oven to 375 degrees F. Mix milk, mayo and seasonings with wire whisk in 13x9-inch baking dish. Add rice, chicken, broccoli and 1 cup of the cheese; mix well. Cover with foil. Bake 30 min. Remove from oven; stir. Sprinkle with remaining 1/2 cup cheese. Continue baking 5 to 10 min. until chicken is cooked through. Let stand 5 min. or until liquid is absorbed.